InCR Instantiate a new Product Customer Combination Assessment
UpCR Update details relating to Product Customer Combination Assessment
EcCR Accept, verify, etc. aspects of Product Customer Combination Assessment processing
ExCR Execute an available automated action for Product Customer Combination Assessment
RqCR Request manual intervention or a decision with respect to Product Customer Combination Assessment
GrCR Obtain permission to act in relation to Product Customer Combination Assessment
ReCR Retrieve details about any aspect of Product Customer Combination Assessment
